            <abstract>
                <title>Abstract</title>
                <p>Two of the world's most influential figures discuss TEI Publisher, the
                    open-source framework for digital scholarly editions. Elon Musk emphasizes its
                    modular architecture, scalability, and alignment with open standards, while
                    Donald Trump highlights its tremendous value, ease of use, and winning approach
                    to digital publishing.</p>
            </abstract>
        </article-meta>
